data.description: This may be the Hobby Farm you have been waiting for!  Over 12 level acres of flood irrigated fenced property for livestock, chickens, gardening, of course your pets and parking or storage for all of your toys. The essentials are already in place with a Barn, Machinery Shed and a Shop/Garage and it's in close proximity to the conveniences of town, schools and outdoor recreation. The driveway is paved leading to your comfortable well maintained 3-bedroom 2 bath home including Stainless Steel appliances, walk in closets in all bedrooms and a front porch to take advantage of the beautiful views. Behind your home on the back of the property an artesian stream meanders along the property line and provides a refuge for pheasants, quail and ducks. Come take a look and enjoy the peaceful views and quiet serenity of this property.
